    <string name="about_text"><![CDATA[
        Hacker News Android app.<br/><br/>
        This is an unofficial Android app for reading Hacker News.<br/><br/>
        Hacker News is a social news website focusing on computer science and entrepreneurship.
        In general, the content is about \"anything that gratifies one\'s intellectual curiosity\".<br/><br/>
        The official website can be found on
        <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com">https://news.ycombinator.com</a><br/><br/>
        This project is open source. Crashes, bugs, or feature requests can be reported on this project\'s
        <a href="https://github.com/marcelje/hacker-news-android-app">Github page</a>.
        Contributors are also welcomed.
    ]]></string>
